\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces The regulatory cycle. Steps 2--4 implement the sequential BIND-remeasure-VEIL protocol: BIND fires first (step\nonbreakingspace 2), the tree is remeasured (step\nonbreakingspace 3), then VEIL fires on the updated structure (step\nonbreakingspace 4). Remeasuring between regulators prevents destructive interference.}}{4}{figure.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:regulatory}{{3}{4}{The regulatory cycle. Steps 2--4 implement the sequential BIND-remeasure-VEIL protocol: BIND fires first (step~2), the tree is remeasured (step~3), then VEIL fires on the updated structure (step~4). Remeasuring between regulators prevents destructive interference}{figure.caption.10}{}}
