\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Convergence traces for four governance scenarios. Blue: coordination. Orange: gatedness. Dashed lines mark health band boundaries (coordination $[0.3, 0.7]$, gatedness $[0.2, 0.6]$). (a)\nonbreakingspace Well-governed converges at cycle\nonbreakingspace 18. (b)\nonbreakingspace Ungoverned oscillates without settling. (c)\nonbreakingspace Over-governed: coordination in band but gatedness stuck at ${\sim }0.14$, below the health band. (d)\nonbreakingspace Drifting: period-2 oscillation crossing band boundaries.}}{6}{figure.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:convergence}{{4}{6}{Convergence traces for four governance scenarios. Blue: coordination. Orange: gatedness. Dashed lines mark health band boundaries (coordination $[0.3, 0.7]$, gatedness $[0.2, 0.6]$). (a)~Well-governed converges at cycle~18. (b)~Ungoverned oscillates without settling. (c)~Over-governed: coordination in band but gatedness stuck at ${\sim }0.14$, below the health band. (d)~Drifting: period-2 oscillation crossing band boundaries}{figure.caption.21}{}}
